Detailed Description

cvmx_tdec::_tc_config_err_flags_reg

This register reports task configuration errors that occur when a specified parameter value is outside the acceptable range. Different bit-mappings are used depending on whether the PHY_MODE is LTE or 3G, and whether the TASK_TYPE is E-DCH or DCH.
